name: "Grasp..." by RFY (HF) & FEH
description: [Felt pen on colored cardstock with digital embellishments and color.] Here is another in a long line of collaborations between me (Richard F. Yates) and my granddaughter (Felicity Echo Hanson). She is a MASTER of CHAOS, and creates wild, energetic lines. (Of course she's only two, so she doesn't REALIZE how great her art is, yet...) And then I come in and carve out a bit of definition in the chaos. My part is making the work less exciting and energetic, but also giving it more of a figurative, "recognizable" face (or "hand" in this case). I think we work well together! (And, yes, I'm putting money from sales away for her college education!!!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Toddler Terror)
